  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleInstances.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=480\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleInstances.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"480\" data-width=\"640\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539829\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesParticleInstances.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"44d50ea3-520b-4208-93d0-dfebcd793e2f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleInstances.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=480 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleInstances.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=480 1x\"></span><p>Reusing geometry through <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN26/pages/19661429\" rel=\"nofollow\">instancing</a> can allow for a tremendous reduction of the memory footprint when rendering complex scenes in RenderMan.  Even when working with simpler scenes that contain multiple similar objects, it can be convenient to incorporate instancing into your workflow.</p><p>In Maya there are several approaches to setting up instances, including:</p><div class=\"toc-macro client-side-toc-macro  conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-headerelements=\"H3\" data-layout=\"default\" data-local-id=\"9c494d0d-b590-4133-9110-0bfe8119e3b8\" data-macro-id=\"53ee1b79-02a9-4875-a897-14e80f6bb47b\" data-macro-name=\"toc\"> </div><h3 id=\"InstancesinMaya-MayaInstances\">Maya Instances</h3><p>Maya instances are probably the most familiar form of instancing in Maya.  Maya instances are rendered as &quot;object instances&quot; in RenderMan, its most efficient form of instancing.</p><p>In this example, suppose a teacup will be instanced.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesStart.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=480\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesStart.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"480\" data-width=\"640\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539823\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesStart.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9c859418-ce52-4122-87ac-9e2bd6b219e7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesStart.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=480 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesStart.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=480 1x\"></span><p>Select the top level group node of the hierarchy that you want to instance, in this case the teacup node.</p><p>If the object that you wish to instance is very complex, you may want to create a <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/RFM27/pages/544539634/Archives+in+Maya\" rel=\"nofollow\">RenderMan Archive</a> first, and instance that, so the original geometry doesn't even have to be present in the scene.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesOutliner.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=275&amp;height=123\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesOutliner.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"123\" data-width=\"275\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539814\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesOutliner.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"258f8765-e04d-4409-9bc7-e4a9a8a85be9\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesOutliner.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=275&amp;height=123 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesOutliner.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=275&amp;height=123 1x\"></span><p>Do Edit-&gt;Duplicate Special, opening the option box.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesDuplicateSpecial.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=304&amp;height=26\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesDuplicateSpecial.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"26\" data-width=\"304\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539808\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesDuplicateSpecial.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ee4ff28b-1685-4742-8272-ec91d6bbed4f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesDuplicateSpecial.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=304&amp;height=26 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesDuplicateSpecial.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549198&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=304&amp;height=26 1x\"></span><p>Make sure instancing is enabled in the options.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesCreateOption.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=263&amp;height=44\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesCreateOption.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"44\" data-width=\"263\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539811\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesCreateOption.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"981d3e8c-50e3-47d1-bba9-e55cf88ac33e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesCreateOption.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=263&amp;height=44 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesCreateOption.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549199&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=263&amp;height=44 1x\"></span><p>A new instance appears in the outliner.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesOutliner2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=275&amp;height=61\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesOutliner2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"61\" data-width=\"275\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539817\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesOutliner2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9f804b31-9fdc-47c9-99c1-7fa5c6b39208\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesOutliner2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=275&amp;height=61 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesOutliner2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=275&amp;height=61 1x\"></span><p>Open the HyperGraph Hierarchy window to observe that original node and the instance are separate transforms that share the same geometry. (Windows-&gt;HyperGraph: Hierarchy)</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesHypergraphHierarchy.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=344&amp;height=132\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesHypergraphHierarchy.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"132\" data-width=\"344\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539820\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesHypergraphHierarchy.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"919f5b61-89bf-4f0a-a09c-b486f7ff2c28\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesHypergraphHierarchy.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=344&amp;height=132 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesHypergraphHierarchy.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549447&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=344&amp;height=132 1x\"></span><p>The new instance can be positioned independently.  </p><h4 id=\"InstancesinMaya-MultipleMaterials\">Multiple Materials</h4><p>New materials can be assigned to the instanced shapes.  Select the shape in the viewport that you want to assign a new material, and assign in your usual manner.  The new material will become assigned only to the shape you clicked on.  </p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstances2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549631&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=480\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstances2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549631&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"480\" data-width=\"640\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539826\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstances2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"998beb36-6dce-4b38-b747-523f3505f90b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstances2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549631&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=480 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstances2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549631&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=640&amp;height=480 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"InstancesinMaya-ParticleInstancer\">Particle Instancer</h3><p>Creating Maya instances and positioning them each independently can become impractical for large numbers of instances.  Maya's particle instancer is one approach to instancing geometry at particles.</p><p>First, create some particles.  This can be done using an emitter (to place particles dynamically) or Maya's nParticle Tool to place individual particles.  Both nParticles and Maya's legacy particles are supported.</p><p>In the example below, particles have been positioned individually using the nParticle Tool.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleTool.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=257&amp;height=516\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleTool.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"516\" data-width=\"257\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539868\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesParticleTool.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d97d3d5c-bdb2-48c3-b840-07fc96ee5c1f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleTool.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=257&amp;height=516 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleTool.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=257&amp;height=516 1x\"></span><p>Note, sometimes when doing particle instancing, you'll get unexpected offsets in Maya.  To avoid this move the object that will be instanced (eg. teacup) to 0,0,0.  Do Modify-&gt;Freeze Transformations.  And so that per particle attributes can be used for each instance, you can leave the original out of the view.</p><p>Looking through the &quot;top&quot; orthographic camera.  Click to create particles where new instances should sit, and when done hit Enter.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticles.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549821&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=238&amp;height=250\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesParticles.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549821&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"250\" data-width=\"238\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539835\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesParticles.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"27281428-e359-4066-ad75-3784f067d64a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticles.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549821&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=238&amp;height=250 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticles.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549821&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=238&amp;height=250 1x\"></span><p>Select the node that should be instanced (eg. teacup) followed by the particle shape's transform (eg. nParticle1), and do nParticles-&gt;Instancer.  If you select these in the wrong order, Maya will point that out.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesInstancer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=257&amp;height=135\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesInstancer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"135\" data-width=\"257\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539871\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesInstancer.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"bb095f16-9d78-4c12-841d-00186db094b0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesInstancer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=257&amp;height=135 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesInstancer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=257&amp;height=135 1x\"></span><p>You'll see an instance appear at each particle position.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"380\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleInstancer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=380&amp;height=268\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleInstancer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539832\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesParticleInstancer.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c8495e3e-04d1-4875-9f64-327e470c6da5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleInstancer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=536 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesParticleInstancer.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431549632&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=380&amp;height=268 1x\"></span> </p><h3 id=\"InstancesinMaya-XGenArchives\">XGen Archives</h3><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"600\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmAttributes.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550868&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=496&amp;height=1018\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmAttributes.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550868&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1018\" data-width=\"496\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539889\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmAttributes.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"06423f8b-c63f-4efb-85f3-4e080080963a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmAttributes.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550868&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=496&amp;height=1018 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmAttributes.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550868&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=496&amp;height=1018 1x\"></span><h4 id=\"InstancesinMaya-NestedInstancing\">Nested Instancing</h4><p>Especially when dealing with large data sets like Xgen instancing of many objects, we try and flatten the instances to allow users flexibility in overrides and improve speed. But there are times when this may consume too much memory. This is because flattened instances multiply when rendered, so 1,000 instances of 1,000 instances are 1,000,000 instances.</p><p>Nested instances are added so 1,000 instances of 1,000 becomes 2,000 in memory. However, options for instances like some variation and more are no longer available to the renderer. So we allows users to decide when to nest instancing in the transform nodes by tagging them.</p><p><br/></p><h4 id=\"InstancesinMaya-CreateXGenDescription\">Create XGen Description</h4><p>XGen is a powerful tool that can be used to position instances of arbitrary geometry.  First an XGen description needs to be created, which holds the collection of points where instances will be placed.  Then, the archive can be created to instance at those points.</p><p>Select the shape upon which instances should be placed (eg. the ground plane).  Then from the XGen toolbar, click on the leftmost icon with an X.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"114\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenButton.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550682&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=37&amp;height=36\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenButton.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550682&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"36\" data-width=\"37\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539883\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesXGenButton.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3be5c179-0c92-44d8-b701-172a66b1ecf4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenButton.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550682&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=37&amp;height=36 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenButton.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550682&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=37&amp;height=36 1x\"></span><p>In the XGen window that pops up, choose the button that says &quot;Create New Description&quot;.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenCreateNew.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=274&amp;height=137\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenCreateNew.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"137\" data-width=\"274\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539874\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesXGenCreateNew.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"77f89325-1952-4f37-8dfd-84e06c61a1ad\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenCreateNew.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=274&amp;height=137 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenCreateNew.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=274&amp;height=137 1x\"></span><p>In the Create XGen Description dialog that pops up, choose the radio button called &quot;Custom Geometry/Archives (use for any model you have created)&quot;.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenCustomGeometry.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=460&amp;height=125\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenCustomGeometry.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"125\" data-width=\"460\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539877\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesXGenCustomGeometry.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"209992d4-4675-4925-9747-bc395fd2f54a\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenCustomGeometry.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=460&amp;height=125 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenCustomGeometry.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550514&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=460&amp;height=125 1x\"></span><p>Go ahead and click the Create button.  This distributes points randomly across the plane.  Don't worry about that now.  Let's create an archive.</p><h4 id=\"InstancesinMaya-CreateXGenArchive\">Create XGen Archive</h4><p>In the XGen Window, under the Primitives tab, scroll down to the section called Archive Files.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenArchiveFilesEmpty.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=505&amp;height=185\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenArchiveFilesEmpty.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"185\" data-width=\"505\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539859\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesXGenArchiveFilesEmpty.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"31a8594e-e4e3-454f-8dfa-53635514c18c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenArchiveFilesEmpty.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=505&amp;height=185 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenArchiveFilesEmpty.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=505&amp;height=185 1x\"></span><p>Select the top level transform of the hierarchy that you wish to archive (eg. teacup node), then click on the button called &quot;Create From Selection...&quot;</p><p>In the &quot;Export Selection as Archives&quot; dialog that comes up, go ahead and choose a location and name for the XGen archive, and Export.  You may also be prompted to re-save the scene.</p><p>Next, click on the &quot;Add...&quot; button below the Archive Files list.  Browse to the previously saved archive.  The file name should end with .xarc.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenArchiveFiles.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=503&amp;height=186\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenArchiveFiles.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"186\" data-width=\"503\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539862\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesXGenArchiveFiles.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"fcbc5498-d7f3-4f6f-b5d1-569e59eed1bf\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenArchiveFiles.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=503&amp;height=186 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenArchiveFiles.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=503&amp;height=186 1x\"></span><p>You should see instances of your archive densely packed across the ground plane.</p><h4 id=\"InstancesinMaya-SpecifyPoints\">Specify Points</h4><p>If random positioning isn't what you're after, you can specify points at specific locations.</p><p>Scroll to the top of the XGen Primitives tab.  Change the Generate Primitives setting from &quot;Randomly across the surface&quot; to &quot;At specified locations.  Then, click on the button that says &quot;Specify Points...&quot;</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenSpecifyPoints.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=484&amp;height=156\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenSpecifyPoints.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"156\" data-width=\"484\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539853\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesXGenSpecifyPoints.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"5cbd277e-af31-493d-a57a-0830bad4cf47\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenSpecifyPoints.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=484&amp;height=156 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenSpecifyPoints.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=484&amp;height=156 1x\"></span><p>A tool appears in the viewport for placing points.</p><p>After placing points, you should see the archive instanced at those points.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenPointsPlaced.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=887&amp;height=654\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenPointsPlaced.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"654\" data-width=\"887\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539856\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesXGenPointsPlaced.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8a8a5e2f-3196-44d2-92e9-c088c6681f00\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenPointsPlaced.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=887&amp;height=654 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenPointsPlaced.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550178&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=887&amp;height=654 1x\"></span><h4 id=\"InstancesinMaya-AddaMaterial\">Add a Material</h4><p>Under the Preview/Output tab, scroll down to the RenderMan Settings section.  Here a new material can be applied to the archvies.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenRenderManSettings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=105\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenRenderManSettings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"105\" data-width=\"497\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544539865\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfmInstancesXGenRenderManSettings.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544539792\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"8993596b-eb8b-4812-b44a-730694531447\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenRenderManSettings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=105 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/544539792/rfmInstancesXGenRenderManSettings.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754431550343&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=497&amp;height=105 1x\"></span><p />"
    }
